parseInventory(Inventory) - Method in class adhdmc.villagerinfo.util.MessageResolvers
Parses the message component for the given Inventory Uses the 'VILLAGER_INVENTORY', 'EMPTY', and 'INVENTORY_CONTENTS' locale messages Uses the placeholders "item" for the name of the item, "value" for how many of the item there is.
parseLocationMessage(String, Location) - Method in class adhdmc.villagerinfo.util.MessageResolvers
Parses the message component for the given string and location.
parseSingleValue(String, String) - Method in class adhdmc.villagerinfo.util.MessageResolvers
Parses a message component for a given string and value Uses the placeholder "value" for the supplied value
parseTimeMessage(String, Long) - Method in class adhdmc.villagerinfo.util.MessageResolvers
Parses the message component for the given string and time difference in seconds Uses the 'NEVER', 'HOUR', 'MINUTE', 'SECOND', 'AGO', and 'JUST_NOW' locale messages Uses the placeholders "value" for the time amounts, and "time" for the final time message insertion
parseTwoValues(String, String, String) - Method in class adhdmc.villagerinfo.util.MessageResolvers
Parses a message component for a given string and two given values Uses the placeholders "value" for the first supplied value, "value2" for the second supplied value
